    var timerId = null,

    function WaitUntilCustomerGUIDIsRetrieved() {
        if ( !! (timerId)) {
            if (timeout == 0) {
                return;
            }
            if (typeof GetElqCustomerGUID === 'function') {
                appendTrackingField();
                return;
            }
            timeout -= 1;
        }
        timerId = setTimeout('WaitUntilCustomerGUIDIsRetrieved()', 500);
        return;
    }

    // add contact GUID to all form submissions
    function appendTrackingField() {
        $('<input type="hidden" id="elqCustomerGUID" name="elqCustomerGUID" />').appendTo($('.FormPanel'))
            .val(GetElqCustomerGUID());
    }

    function getCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + ' = ';
        var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
        for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++)
        {
            var c = ca[i];
            while (c.charAt(0) == ' ')
            {
                c = c.substring(1);
            }
            if (c.indexOf(name) == 0)
            {
                return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
            }
        }
        return '';
    }

        <script>
         $(document).ready(function () {
        var puzzlePieces = $('.puzzle-piece');
        var puzzlePieceContent = $('.puzzle-piece .content');

        setTimeout(function () {
            $(".hero-top").addClass('animate');

            setTimeout(function () {
                $(".hero-top .overlay .lock-up").addClass('animate');
            }, 500);

            setTimeout(function () {
                $("#home-hero").addClass('animate'); //swoosh fade

                //puzzle pieces
                setTimeout(function () {
                    $(puzzlePieces[1]).addClass('animate');
                }, 250);

                setTimeout(function () {
                    $(puzzlePieces[0]).addClass('animate');
                }, 500);

                setTimeout(function () {
                    $(puzzlePieces[2]).addClass('animate');

                    setTimeout(function () {
                        $(puzzlePieceContent).addClass('animate');


                        setTimeout(function () {
                            $('.two-col-text').addClass('animate');
                        }, 200);

                        var timeoutInterval;
                        $('.icons .column').each(function (k, v) {
                            timeoutInterval = k * 200
                            var that = $(this);
                            setTimeout(function () {
                                that.addClass('animate');
                            }, timeoutInterval);
                            setTimeout(function () {
                                that.find('img').addClass('animate');
                            }, timeoutInterval);
                            setTimeout(function () {
                                that.find('p').addClass('animate');
                            }, timeoutInterval * 2); //fade image text in after icons cascading
                        });

                        setTimeout(function () {
                            $(".new-stamp").addClass('animate'); //stamp
                        }, 1500);

                        setTimeout(function () {
                            $('.cta-button').addClass('animate');
                        },2000);

                    }, 250);


                }, 500);



            }, 750);

        }, 0);

    });
        </script>
